1 Hour Ago Here are a few things to know about the new army boss:1. Before his appointment, he was the Theatre Commander of the counter-terrorism military outfit in the North-East which is code-named operation Hadin Kai. 2. Yahaya was the former General Officer Commanding 1 Division of the Nigerian Army, Kaduna. 3. He is a a member of Regular Course 37. 4. He is from Zamfara State. 5. He is the 22nd Chief of Army Staff. 6. He has also held the position of Military Secretary (Army). 7. He was also Commander of 4 Brigade Headquarters of the Nigerian Army in Benin, Edo State.